summary: An ordinance to license and regulate secondhand dealers in the City of Seattle, providing penalties for the violation thereof and repealing Sections 66 to 71, inclusive, of Ordinance No. 15855 entitled: "An ordinance to license and regulate certain trades and occupations in the City of Seattle and providing penalties for the violation thereof, approved April 25, 1907", and repealing Ordinance No. 24997 entitled: "An ordinance amending Section 67 of Ordinance No. 15855 entitled 'An ordinance to license and regulate certain trades and occupations in the City of Seattle, and providing penalties for violation thereof."
